OL,4,CFestivals face 'another lost summer'
OL,5,Cwithout government safety net, MPs say
OL,6, UK music festivals face "another lost
OL,7, summer" due to the government's refusal
OL,8, to back insurance for events at risk, a
OL,9, committee of MPs has found.
OL,11,FA report into the sector's future said
OL,12,Fthe government should provide a safety
OL,13,Fnet for live events set to take place
OL,14,Fafter 21 June.
OL,16,FSeveral major festivals have been axed
OL,17,Ffor the second year running.
OL,19,FThe government said it was "continuing
OL,20,Fto work flat out to support festivals
OL,21,Fand live events".
